Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:04.02,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Charybdis, the calamity, has awakened,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:07.01,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and it's heading straight \Ntoward the capital city of Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:11.20,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I'm the one \Nit's after... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.71,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The forces we have ready \Nto go up against Charybdis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.22,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,are Benimaru's group, \NGobta and the Goblin riders,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.93,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,the High Orcs led by Geld,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.47,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Gabiru and his men,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.48,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and some help sent by King Gazel:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.44,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,100 Pegasus Knights, \Nled by the knight captain Dorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:39.97,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Their presence here is definitely reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:47.36,Main,Gazel,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that I help \Nmy junior in his time of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:48.50,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:55.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, King Gazel likes \Nto think of himself as my senior...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:59.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:00.19,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.01,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,That {\c&H471E13&}Time {\c&HCD9612&}I Got {\c&H471E13&}Reincarnated {\c&HCD9612&}as a {\c&H7E4F0A&}Slime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.26,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1315,0)}Episode 19: Charybdis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.02,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this! Hell Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.52,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Benimaru. \NHe toasted that thing to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:56.41,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's shocking that even his attack \Nwasn't enough to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.60,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Is that one of Charybdis's skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:02:59.59,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:02:59.62,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(322,1)}Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.12,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,With the extra skill Magic Jamming,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:07.67,sign_4316_26_Magic_Jamming,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)}Magic\NJamming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:05.87,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,the movement of magicules in a \N300-meter radius is disturbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.67,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,reducing the efficacy of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.97,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy's going to be trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Stick to the plan! Scatter them \Nand strike each one individually!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:23.21,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop it from moving! All of you, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.56,Main,Orc,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Geld!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.24,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.74,Italics,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.69,Italics,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades can't do anything \Nnow, so to attack this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:49.59,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:52.87,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Vortex Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.93,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Gabiru, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:03:59.61,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.65,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Tend to the wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.68,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,We're on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:07.57,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Since you stopped it, I had a \Nmuch easier time taking it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.11,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the assistance, Gabiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.95,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring that one down! \NYou can take it from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.70,Main,Geld,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll stop it myself this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:22.20,Main,Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Gabiru, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.29,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,On the pride of the Pegasus Knights, \Nwe will stop them here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.80,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.96,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,Some will divert, others will attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.81,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,Enter this battle with a clear \Nunderstanding of your own role...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.57,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,and without fear of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.57,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hakurou's such a pro at giving orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.58,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Regaining his youth has allowed him \Nto refine his tough teaching style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.94,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wanna play, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:09.75,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here? \NDidn't I tell you to wait back in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.59,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can watch, at least, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:14.34,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Staying in town is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.09,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'll just—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.47,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at me like that won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.46,Main,Soka,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Master Souei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:26.89,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.77,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Puppet Strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:42.66,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He's manipulating the Megalodons \Nto make them fight each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:46.16,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Anything goes for that dreamboat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.42,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for the right moment, then kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.60,Main,Soka,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:04.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They're flying? When did Ranga learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.43,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, when did he team up with Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:11.06,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I must play an active role \Nand stand out this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.94,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.24,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Decapitating Demon Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.24,sign_9129_73_Decapitating_Dem,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Decapitating Demon Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.91,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Let me, too! Let me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.00,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.26,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that just leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:47.02,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see just how strong it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.27,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.57,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:08.20,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,You have improved a bit, but to think \Nyou couldn't even stop one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.44,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,You will need much tougher training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:14.84,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anything tougher than this \Nis gonna kill me, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:15.96,Main,Hakurou,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.11,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.56,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So all that's left now is Charybdis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.17,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,With his ability, it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.56,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.82,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That thing sure is huge, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:42.87,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.03,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.95,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from its size, the—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:45.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.86,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna say something, \Ntell me the easiest way to beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.58,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now she shuts up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're not even leaving a mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:58.96,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:03.96,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,It might try to pull something! \NDon't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:04.84,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.59,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.93,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.19,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Evade! Get away from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.76,Italics,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,I can't dodge them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.64,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge? Don't be a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:05.28,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Souei, use Shadow Movement to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.78,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,I will act as Shion's shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:10.17,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Do you want to die, Ranga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.16,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:18.17,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama's chosen course of action is the \None granting the highest chance of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.38,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Highest chance of survival, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.04,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll stay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.34,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.43,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,The real me will withdraw before \NI get killed, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.41,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Typical Souei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.93,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let us all survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.04,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really are idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.28,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least rely \Non me at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.54,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Devour all! Gluttony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.51,Italics,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,All those scales, in a mere instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:12.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me. \NYou guys fall back and rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.06,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,We can still help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The scales are starting to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.07,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The next time it uses those,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:30.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll be \Nable to protect you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:34.08,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight it for a while. \NAttack at Benimaru's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.45,Main,Souei,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.71,Main,Shion,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Rimuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.95,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I will return to help you shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:53.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I guess I'll \Njust do whatever I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it actually hurting... a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does this thing have Rapid Regeneration?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.71,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(151,437)}Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:21.53,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.08,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the speed at which \Nit repairs its body tissue,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.79,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,there is no doubt that \Nthe individual Charybdis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:30.26,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,possesses the extra skill \N"Ultraspeed Regeneration."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:30.26,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(363,1)\3c&H000000&\c&H130065&\fs16\b1}Extra Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.26,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(197,1)\3c&H000000&\c&H060096&\an8\fs30\pos(320,128)}Ultraspeed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:30.26,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(319,1)\3c&H000000&\c&H060096&\an2\fs30\pos(320,232)}Regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:35.10,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Using Ultraspeed Regeneration, \Nit is estimated that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.18,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,it will regenerate all its \Nscales within three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:41.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So we have three minutes before a \Nrepeat of what it did earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.07,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, utilize all methods at \Nyour disposal to attack Charybdis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.32,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the effects are weak! \NDon't give it a chance to recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.33,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:03.33,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The support of the Pegasus Knights \Nincreased our strength more than tenfold,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:08.05,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,so we thought we'd take down \Nwith an all-out attack, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.62,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I think Charybdis is damaged \Nby about 30% at most...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:24.29,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,An all-out attack managed 30%... \NThis is looking bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.58,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.42,Main,Charybdis,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:34.31,Main,Charybdis,0000,0000,0000,,M-Milim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.11,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Milim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.88,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You just said "Milim," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.87,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Great Sage, use Appraisal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:41.79,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(737,1)\3c&H190E0E&}Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:41.87,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:45.72,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Signs of life confirmed from the \Nbody that Charybdis has occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:49.38,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,The body appears to possess intense anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.38,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H362919&\3c&HD7E2E8&\t(27,68,1 \c&H5F5408&)\t(69,110,1 \3c&H8776CC&)\t(111,151,1 \c&HACB010&\3c&H5A3DC0&)\t(152,193,1 \3c&H07009C&)\t(194,235,1 \c&HDBE5E2&\3c&H111111&)\t(735,1861,1\c&H0B00A0&\3c&HDBE0E7&)}Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Intense anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.75,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Toward Milim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:59.23,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, Charybdis headed toward \Nour town because Milim was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:03.39,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it had figured out \Nthat Veldora was inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.64,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.81,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:09.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I depend on Milim for this, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:11.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.07,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Milim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.95,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't asleep! I was awake the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were obviously asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.33,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I was just meditating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.70,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I was really cheering you guys on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, this guy seems to \Nhave business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.21,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:37.24,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's using that guy who came \Ninto town, Phobio, as its physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:39.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That guy? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:45.60,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I had you sit this one out because \NI thought he was after me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:48.73,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna say I can fight him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:57.09,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,He was here for you, and we were \Njust in the way. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:59.42,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.32,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Phobio works for the \NDemon Lord Carrion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.00,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like to let him \Nlive and help him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.11,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.75,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how much restraint \NI've learned recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.79,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Restraint?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.13,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Does she really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.05,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:33.48,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Mili... Milim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:40.01,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I've already seen that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.49,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll show you one of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.29,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:53.25,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,what you call "restraint"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.76,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Drago Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.49,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is the "restraint"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.66,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That was some nice restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:54.60,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:16:00.15,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,The magicore of Charybdis has been \Nremoved from Phobio and consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.74,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Preparing to isolate it and begin Appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.74,sign_4291_23_Notice,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(689,1)\c&HD0C2DE&\3c&H8A16A6&}Appraisal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.44,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.86,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dorf-san. I appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:20.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to defeat \NCharybdis thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:24.26,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't us who defeated Charybdis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.76,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Could you explain what this is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:33.27,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,this girl is called \NDemon Lord Milim, and... you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.68,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.57,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have a fondness for jokes, Rimuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:49.33,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,If you had such a powerful magical weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.96,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you had said so from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.06,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke! I'm a Demon Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:57.43,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I defeated Charybdis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:01.45,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You wish to keep the \Nspecifics of your weapon secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.94,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.65,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,It's always best to keep \Nyour trump card hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.64,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I'm a Demon Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.81,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,Charybdis could have had catastrophic \Neffects on all mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:13.43,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,so its defeat is most fortuitous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:17.93,Main,Dorf,0000,0000,0000,,I must report to my king, \Nso I will take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.06,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You were a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Give King Gazel my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.16,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.42,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:37.51,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,What... What did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.81,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.82,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:48.34,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,I've done something \Nunthinkable to Lady Milim,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:51.22,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,and I've caused so much trouble for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.46,Main,Treyni,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know where Charybdis was sealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.98,Main,Trya,0000,0000,0000,,We won't accept that you \Njust happened to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:17:59.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.44,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Right... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.03,Main,Treyni,0000,0000,0000,,Masked harlequins named Tear and Footman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.77,Main,Treyni,0000,0000,0000,,Did the mask look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:15.70,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,No, the ones I met were a girl in \Na mask with a tear under one eye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.12,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,and a heavy man with an angry mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.13,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.20,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,That Laplace guy also..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.35,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Laplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:29.13,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Laplace once showed up before \Nme as a servant of Gelmud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.39,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,He was wearing a mask like \Nthe one Treyni described.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:38.58,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he called himself the vice \Npresident of a jack-of-all-trades group
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.53,Main,Gabiru,0000,0000,0000,,called the Moderate Harlequin Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.65,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now the dots are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.21,Main,Treyni,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:47.27,Main,Treyni,0000,0000,0000,,And this person's name was Laplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.09,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Footman, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.53,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to remember that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:54.41,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.43,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious jack-of-all-trades group, \Nthe Moderate Harlequin Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They pretend they're helping you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:04.42,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,then use you to fulfill their goals \Nwithout getting their own hands dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.60,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They sound like they'll be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.18,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:13.80,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if fun people like that are \Nreally out there, I wanna meet them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:18.16,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,It may be that it wasn't Gelmud,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:22.57,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,but Clayman who's plotting \Nsomething in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:23.81,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Clayman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.41,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,He loves coming up with schemes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.74,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord Clayman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.70,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of whose scheme I was roped into,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.44,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,what happened was my own responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.43,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with Demon \NLord Carrion, so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.46,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Take my life and leave him out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:46.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, be more on your toes \Nso you won't be fooled again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:47.88,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You can move now, right? So you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.91,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,But... what I did was unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.22,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.63,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Milim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.63,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.62,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd give him just one little whack,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.73,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,but I've matured so much, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.88,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:10.05,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad at all, so I forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.16,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:13.25,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.81,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay with you, right, Carrion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.19,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Carrion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.22,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,So you figured it out, Milim?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.50,Main,Milim,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.69,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy is the Demon Lord Carrion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.00,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:33.26,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for sparing this guy's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:40.04,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,You're the masked majin who \Ndefeated Gelmud, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.90,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to avenge him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.85,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.99,Main,Phobio,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.29,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.07,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.48,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my underling \Nhere was out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.88,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,That means I was negligent in his oversight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.40,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.88,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.74,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one after all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.88,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,If anything comes up, \Nyou can always count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:22.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd appreciate it if you'd \Nenter a non-aggression pact with our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.86,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you want? Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.06,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:33.16,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,The Beastmaster of the Animal \NKingdom of Eurazania, Carrion,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:36.07,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,swears on his name to never \Nraise a blade to your nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.27,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.32,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.90,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.29,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, he's losing tons of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:48.32,Main,Carrion,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you again, Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.43,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:03.33,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.54,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Yuuki Kagurazaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:40.03,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(358,1)}Yuuki Kagurazaka

